Package org.hibernate.engine.spi

Interface SessionFactoryImplementor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, jakarta.persistence.EntityManagerFactory, HibernateEntityManagerFactory, Mapping, QueryParameterBindingTypeResolver, Referenceable, Serializable, SessionFactory, SqlAstCreationContext, SqmCreationContext
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SessionFactoryDelegatingImpl, SessionFactoryImpl
    public interface SessionFactoryImplementor
extends Mapping, SessionFactory, SqmCreationContext, SqlAstCreationContext, QueryParameterBindingTypeResolver
    Defines the internal contract between the SessionFactory and other parts of Hibernate such as implementors of Type.
    See Also:
    SessionFactory, SessionFactoryImpl
